===再生能力===
斑马鱼在幼鱼阶段能够[[再生|再生]]其鳍、皮肤、心脏、[[体侧线|体侧线]]的[[毛细胞|毛细胞]]以及大脑。<ref name=Wade>{{cite news |title=Research Offers Clue Into How Hearts Can Regenerate in Some Species |last=Wade |first=Nicholas |work=The New York Times |date=March 24, 2010 |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2010/03/25/science/25heart.html |accessdate=2018-02-04 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109042237/http://www.nytimes.com/2010/03/25/science/25heart.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="autogenerated1187">{{cite journal |last=Lush |first=Mark E. |last2=Piotrowski |first2=Tatjana |year=2013 |title=Sensory hair cell regeneration in the zebrafish lateral line |journal=Developmental Dynamics |volume=243 |issue=10 |pages=1187–1202 |doi=10.1002/dvdy.24167|pmid=25045019 |pmc=4177345}}</ref>在2011年，{{link-en|英国心脏基金会|British Heart Foundation}}广告宣传以公布其将这项能力应用于人体的企划，以期筹措5,000万英镑。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=djFb8PGS34g |title=Mending Broken Hearts (2011) British Heart Foundation TV ad |publisher={{link-en|British Heart Foundation|British Heart Foundation}} via [[YouTube|YouTube]] |date=January 31, 2011 |accessdate=November 15, 2012 |archive-date=2017-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170410213928/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=djFb8PGS34g |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bhf.org.uk/research/mending-broken-hearts-appeal/the-science.aspx?pid=p&sc_cid=MBH-EX-24&gclid=CL2w_L2hhqcCFcgf4QodBA25eA |title=British Heart Foundation – The science behind the appeal |publisher=Bhf.org.uk |date=February 16, 2007 |accessdate=November 15, 2012 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120310000952/http://www.bhf.org.uk/research/mending-broken-hearts-appeal/the-science.aspx?pid=p&sc_cid=MBH-EX-24&gclid=CL2w_L2hhqcCFcgf4QodBA25eA |archivedate=10 March 2012 }}</ref>

斑马鱼也被发现可在创伤后再生[[感光细胞|感光细胞]]与[[视网膜|视网膜]]神经。目前研究显示，这是由{{link-en|米勒细胞|Muller glia}}(Muller glia)的去分化与增殖介导的。<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1523/JNEUROSCI.1624-07.2007 |title=Late-Stage Neuronal Progenitors in the Retina Are Radial Muller Glia That Function as Retinal Stem Cells |year=2007 |last1=Bernardos |first1=Rebecca L. |last2=Barthel |first2=Linda K. |last3=Meyers |first3=Jason R. |last4=Raymond |first4=Pamela A. |journal=Journal of Neuroscience |volume=27 |issue=26 |pages=7028–40 |pmid=17596452}}</ref>研究人员不断[[截肢|截断]]背上以及腹面上的尾鳍，并且分析其再生以观测其突变。已经发现，{{link-en|组蛋白去甲基化酶|Histone methylation}}在截肢部位出现，使得斑马鱼的细胞重新活跃为可再生的类似于干细胞的状态。<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1073/pnas.0904132106 |laysummary=http://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2009/11/091102171419.htm |laysource=Science Daily |laydate=November 2, 2009 |title=A histone demethylase is necessary for regeneration in zebrafish |year=2009 |last1=Stewart |first1=Scott |last2=Tsun |first2=Zhi-Yang |last3=Izpisua Belmonte |first3=Juan Carlos |journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences |pmid=19897725 |jstor=25593294 |pmc=2785262 |volume=106 |issue=47 |pages=19889–94|bibcode=2009PNAS..10619889S }}</ref>2012年，澳洲科学家发布的一项研究表明，斑马鱼使用一种被称为[[成纤维细胞生长因子|成纤维细胞生长因子]]的特异的蛋白质以确保其[[脊髓|脊髓]]可以痊愈而无{{link-en|胶质瘢痕|glial scar}}。<ref name=Regen2012>{{cite journal |pmid=22649227 |laysummary=http://www.sci-news.com/othersciences/biochemistry/article00366.html |laysource=Sci-News.com |laydate=June 1, 2012 |year=2012 |last1=Goldshmit |first1=Yona |last2=Sztal |first2=Tamar E. |last3=Jusuf |first3=Patricia R. |last4=Hall |first4=Thomas E. |last5=Nguyen-Chi |first5=Mai |last6=Currie |first6=Peter D. |title=Fgf-Dependent Glial Cell Bridges Facilitate Spinal Cord Regeneration in Zebrafish |volume=32 |issue=22 |pages=7477–92 |doi=10.1523/JNEUROSCI.0758-12.2012 |journal=The Journal of Neuroscience}}</ref>此外，斑马鱼后侧[[体侧线|体侧线]]的[[毛细胞|毛细胞]]被发现可以在创伤后或者发育中断后再生。<ref name="autogenerated1187"/><ref name="autogenerated832">{{cite journal |last=Head |first=J.R. |last2=Gacioch |first2=L. |last3= Pennisi|last4=Meyers |first4=J.R. |year=2013 |title=Activation of canonical Wnt/B-catenin signaling stimulates proliferation in neuromasts in the zebrafish posterior lateral line |journal=Developmental Dynamics |volume=242 |issue=7 |pages=832–846 |doi=10.1002/dvdy.23973|pmid=23606225 }}</ref>对其再生期间基因表达的研究使得若干重要的信号通路得以被识别出来，例如[[Wnt信号通路|Wnt信号通路]]和[[成纤维细胞生长因子|成纤维细胞生长因子]]等。<ref name="autogenerated832"/><ref>{{cite journal |last=Steiner |first=A.B. |year=2014 |title=Dynamic gene expression by putative hair-cell progenitors during regeneration in the zebrafish lateral line |journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America |volume=111 |issue=14 |pages=1392–1401|author2=and others |displayauthors=1 |bibcode=2014PNAS..111E1393S |last3=Cabot |first3=V. |last4=Hudspeth |first4=A. J. |doi=10.1073/pnas.1318692111 |pmid=24706895 |pmc=3986164}}</ref>

研究包括神经退行性疾病、行动失调、精神疾病、耳聋等在内的神经系统疾病时，研究人员使用斑马鱼来理解遗传学缺陷如何引起人脑、脊椎、感应器功能上的异常。科研人员也通过此途径深入了解人体错综复杂的肌肉与骨骼疾病，例如[[肌肉萎縮症|肌肉萎縮症]]等。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hmg.oxfordjournals.org/content/12/suppl_2/R265.full|title=The zebrafish as a model for muscular dystrophy and congenital myopathy|work=Human Molecular Genetics|date=August 8, 2003|accessdate=March 6, 2013|archive-date=2015-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150909035851/http://hmg.oxfordjournals.org/content/12/suppl_2/R265.full|dead-url=no}}</ref>斑马鱼研究的另一焦点在于理解[[刺猬信号通路|刺猬信号通路]]（一种生物信号）如何影响细胞生长乃至引起一系列的癌症。

===遗传特性===
====基因表达====
由于斑马鱼的生命周期较短、可控性强，故常被用作遗传学研究的模型动物。[[基因敲落|基因敲落]]和用[[義_(分子生物學)|反義]][[嗎啉基|嗎啉基]]进行修改[[RNA剪接|RNA剪接]]是常用的{{link-en|反向遗传学|reverse genetics}}技术。人工合成的[[高分子|高分子]][[嗎啉基|嗎啉基]][[寡核苷酸|寡核苷酸]](MO)包含与DNA、RNA相同的[[核苷|核苷]]；通过与互补序列结合，他们可以减少特定基因的[[基因表現|表达]]或者阻碍其它RNA上进行的过程。[[嗎啉基|嗎啉基]][[寡核苷酸|寡核苷酸]](MO)可以在32细胞阶段后注入胚胎内的某个细胞，使得这一细胞所分裂出的细胞都出现在某个基因上的表达减弱；不过，大分子可以任意透膜通行早期胚胎（小于32细胞）中的细胞中，进行扩散。<ref name=blast2>{{cite journal |doi=10.1016/0012-1606(85)90010-7 |title=Cell lineage of zebrafish blastomeres |year=1985 |last1=Kimmel |first1=Charles B. |last2=Law |first2=Robert D. |journal=Developmental Biology |volume=108 |pages=78–85 |pmid=3972182 |issue=1}}</ref><ref name=blast4>{{cite journal |doi=10.1016/0012-1606(85)90012-0 |title=Cell lineage of zebrafish blastomeres |year=1985 |last1=Kimmel |first1=Charles B. |last2=Law |first2=Robert D. |journal=Developmental Biology |volume=108 |pages=94–101 |pmid=3972184 |issue=1}}</ref>使用[[嗎啉基|嗎啉基]]的指南描述了合理控制策略。<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1371/journal.pgen.1007000 |title=Guidelines for morpholino use in zebrafish |year=2017 |last1=Stainier |first1=DYR |last2=Raz |first2=E |last3=Lawson |first3=ND |last4=Ekker |first4=SC |last5=Burdine |first5=RD |last6=Eisen |first6=JS |last7=Ingham |first7=PW |last8=Schulte-Merker |first8=S |last9=Yelon |first9=D |last10=Weinstein |first10=BM |last11=Mullins |first11=MC |last12=Wilson |first12=SW |last13=Ramakrishnan |first13=L |last14=Amacher |first14=SL |last15=Neuhauss |first15=SCF |last16=Meng |first16=A |last17=Mochizuki |first17=N |last18=Panula |first18=P |last19=Moens |first19=CB |journal=PLoS Genetics |volume=13 |issue=10 |pages=e1007000 |pmid=29049395}}</ref>嗎啉基常以500pL剂量直接通过显微注射注入1～2细胞阶段的斑马鱼胚胎中，使之可以与多数细胞融合。<ref>https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2762901/</ref>

斑马鱼基因敲除的难点在于：基因组在完成[[輻鰭魚|輻鰭魚]]和[[肉鳍鱼|肉鳍鱼]]的分化之后的基因[[复制|复制]]中，由于同源基因互补，[[同源|同源]]基因中其中之一很难不被表达。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hindawi.com/journals/bmri/2012/350352/|title=In Vivo Testing of MicroRNA-Mediated Gene Knockdown in Zebrafish|work=Journal of Biomedicine and Biotechnology|publisher=Hindawi|year=2012|accessdate=July 3, 2013|archive-date=2019-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191130191320/https://www.hindawi.com/journals/bmri/2012/350352/|dead-url=no}}</ref>尽管斑马鱼的[[基因組|基因組]]很复杂，市面上还是不少有供研究[[基因表达谱|基因表达谱]]以分析基因表达的国际化的商业平台的，并且还推荐使用{{link-en|ChIP-on-chip|ChIP-on-chip}}技术的规范。<ref>{{Cite journal|pmid=14500831|title=Evaluation of gene expression measurements from commercial microarray platforms|publisher=NCBI|year=2003|pmc=206463|volume=31|issue=19|journal=Nucleic Acids Res.|pages=5676–84|doi=10.1093/nar/gkg763|author1=Tan|first1=P. K.|last2=Downey|first2=T. J.|last3=Spitznagel Jr|first3=E. L.|last4=Xu|first4=P|last5=Fu|first5=D|last6=Dimitrov|first6=D. S.|last7=Lempicki|first7=R. A.|last8=Raaka|first8=B. M.|last9=Cam|first9=M. C.}}</ref>

====基因组测序====
{{link-en|维康信托基金会桑格研究所|Wellcome Trust Sanger Institute}}在2001年启动斑马鱼基因组测序项目。蒂宾根参考样品系的基因组序列可以在[[美国国家生物技术信息中心|美国国家生物技术信息中心]](NCBI)的[https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/genome?term=danio%20rerio 斑马鱼基因组] {{Wayback|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/genome?term=danio%20rerio |date=20200426095444 }}上获得。斑马鱼参考基因组被注是[[Ensembl|Ensembl]][http://www.ensembl.org/Danio_rerio/Info/Index 项目] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ensembl.org/Danio_rerio/Info/Index |date=20200623131037 }}的一部分，由{{link-en|基因组参考联合会|Genome Reference Consortium}}（Genome Reference Consortium）所维护。<ref>{{cite web|title=Genome Reference Consortium|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/projects/genome/assembly/grc/|publisher=GRC|accessdate=October 23, 2012|archive-date=2016-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161005062544/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/projects/genome/assembly/grc/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2009年，印度[[德里|德里]]的{{link-en|基因组和整合生物学研究所|Institute of Genomics and Integrative Biology}}（Institute of Genomics and Integrative Biology）宣布了一种野生品系斑马鱼的基因组测序，其包含大约17亿对碱基。<ref>[http://www.indianexpress.com/news/Decoding-the-Genome-Mystery/485122 "Decoding the Genome Mystery"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.indianexpress.com/news/Decoding-the-Genome-Mystery/485122 |date=20090715190646 }}. ''[[印度快報|Indian Express]]''. July 5, 2009. Retrieved February 5, 2013.</ref><ref>[http://genome.igib.res.in/ FishMap Zv8] {{Wayback|url=http://genome.igib.res.in/ |date=20180719084933 }}. {{link-en|Institute of Genomics and Integrative Biology|Institute of Genomics and Integrative Biology}} (IGIB). Retrieved June 7, 2012.</ref>野生型斑马鱼的基因组测序差异倍数为39。与参照基因组的比较分析发现了超过500万单核酸突变和超过160万插入或剪切突变。共1.4GB超过26,000个蛋白质编码基因的斑马鱼参照基因组序列由Kerstin Howe等人于2013年发布。<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Howe | first1 = Kerstin | display-authors = 1 | last2 = et al | year = 2013 | title = The zebrafish reference genome sequence and its relationship to the human genome | url = http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/vaop/ncurrent/full/nature12111.html | journal = Nature | volume = 496 | issue = 7446 | pages = 498–503 | doi = 10.1038/nature12111 | pmid = 23594743 | bibcode = 2013Natur.496..498H | pmc = 3703927 | access-date = 2018-02-04 | archive-date = 2014-03-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140308193829/http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/vaop/ncurrent/full/nature12111.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>

====线粒体DNA====
在2001年10月，美國[[奧克拉荷馬大學|奧克拉荷馬大學]]研究人员公开了斑马鱼的完整[[线粒体DNA|线粒体DNA]]序列。<ref name=2001Journal>{{cite journal |first1=Richard E. |last1=Broughton |first2=Jami E. |last2=Milam |first3=Bruce A. |last3=Roe |title=The Complete Sequence of the Zebrafish (''Danio rerio'') Mitochondrial Genome and Evolutionary Patterns in Vertebrate Mitochondrial DNA |journal=Genome Research |pmid=11691861 |pmc=311132 |doi=10.1101/gr.156801 |url=http://genome.cshlp.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=11691861 |year=2001 |volume=11 |issue=11 |pages=1958–67 |doi-broken-date=2017-10-25 |access-date=2018-02-04 |archive-date=2019-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190913084710/https://genome.cshlp.org/content/11/11/1958.long |dead-url=no }}</ref>这一序列包含16,596个碱基对，与其它鱼类差别不超过100个碱基对，仅仅比[[金鱼|金鱼]]([[双名法|双名法]]：''Carassius auratus'')的长18个碱基对，比{{link-en|鲤鱼|carp}}(双名法：''Cyprinus carpio'')的长21个碱基对。其线粒体基因含量与基因顺序与常见的[[脊椎动物|脊椎动物]]线粒体DNA相同，包含13种[[蛋白质|蛋白质]]编码基因和1个包含重链[[复制起点|复制起点]]的非编码控制区。其中间发现有，共5个的1组[[转运核糖核酸|tRNA]]基因和类似脊椎动物轻链复制起点的序列。因为从碱基对变化的角度很难得出有关[[适应性（生物学）|适应性]]的结论，所以很难得出进化上的结论<ref name=2001Journal/>。

====色素基因====
1999年，''nacre''变异在斑马鱼体内的哺乳类同源基因''MITF''传输因子中被识别出来。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Lister|first1=J.A.|last2=Robertson|first2=C.P.|last3=Lepage|first3=T.|last4=Johnson|first4=S.L.|last5=Raible|first5=D.W.|title=nacre encodes a zebrafish microphthalmia-related protein that regulates neural-crest-derived pigment cell fate|journal=Development|volume=126|pages=3757–3767|pmid=10433906|issue=17|date=Sep 1999}}</ref>人体''{{link-en|MITF|MITF}}''的变异会导致眼部缺陷和色素缺失，这一症状是[[瓦登伯革氏症候群|瓦登伯革氏症候群]]的一种。2005年12月，对''golden''品系的研究认为一种被称为{{link-en|SLC24A5|SLC24A5}}的[[溶液|溶质]]载体蛋白编码基因导致了其不同寻常的体色，这种蛋白似乎在[[黑色素|黑色素]]形成过程中是必要的，并且通过马琳代（Morpholino）[[基因剔除|敲除]]，其这一功能被确认。随后，与人体{{tsl|en|Orthologue|直系同源|直系同源的}}基因在实验中被识别出来：一个单碱基对差异被发现能够大大影响肤色，使得浅肤色的欧洲裔人种与黑肤色的非裔人种被区分开来，但这一实验并未对人做实验，而是采用了[[比较基因组学|比较基因组学]]这一新领域的研究方法。<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1126/science.1116238 |title=SLC24A5, a Putative Cation Exchanger, Affects Pigmentation in Zebrafish and Humans |year=2005 |last1=Lamason |first1=R. L. |journal=Science |volume=310 |issue=5755 |pages=1782–6 |pmid=16357253 |last2=Mohideen |first2=MA |last3=Mest |first3=JR |last4=Wong |first4=AC |last5=Norton |first5=HL |last6=Aros |first6=MC |last7=Jurynec |first7=MJ |last8=Mao |first8=X |last9=Humphreville |first9=VR|last10=Humbert |first10=J. E. |last11=Sinha |first11=S |last12=Moore |first12=J. L. |last13=Jagadeeswaran |first13=P |last14=Zhao |first14=W |last15=Ning |first15=G |last16=Makalowska |first16=I |last17=McKeigue |first17=P. M. |last18=O'Donnell |first18=D |last19=Kittles |first19=R |last20=Parra |first20=E. J. |last21=Mangini |first21=N. J. |last22=Grunwald |first22=D. J. |last23=Shriver |first23=M. D. |last24=Canfield |first24=V. A. |last25=Cheng |first25=K. C. |display-authors=8 |bibcode=2005Sci...310.1782L }}</ref>带有''nacre''突变的斑马鱼与带''roy orbison (roy)''突变的斑马鱼交配可以得到没有黑素细胞和虹细胞的斑马鱼，这些得到的斑马鱼在成年期也是透明的，一律有着带颜色的眼睛和半透明的皮肤。<ref name=zviv>{{cite journal |doi=10.1016/j.stem.2007.11.002 |laysummary=http://www.livescience.com/animals/080206-see-thru-fish.html |laysource=LiveScience |laydate=February 6, 2008 |title=Transparent Adult Zebrafish as a Tool for in Vivo Transplantation Analysis |year=2008 |last1=White |first1=Richard Mark |last2=Sessa |first2=Anna |last3=Burke |first3=Christopher |last4=Bowman |first4=Teresa |last5=Leblanc |first5=Jocelyn |last6=Ceol |first6=Craig |last7=Bourque |first7=Caitlin |last8=Dovey |first8=Michael |last9=Goessling |first9=Wolfram |last10=Burns |first10=Caroline Erter |last11=Zon |first11=Leonard I. |journal=Cell Stem Cell |volume=2 |issue=2 |pages=183–9 |pmid=18371439 |pmc=2292119|display-authors=8 }}</ref>

====转基因====
转基因是一种研究斑马鱼基因的功能的常见手段。通过使用Tol2转位子体系的方法，构建转基因品种斑马鱼尤其容易。<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1016/j.devcel.2004.06.005 |title=A Transposon-Mediated Gene Trap Approach Identifies Developmentally Regulated Genes in Zebrafish |year=2004 |last1=Kawakami |first1=Koichi |last2=Takeda |first2=Hisashi |last3=Kawakami |first3=Noriko |last4=Kobayashi |first4=Makoto |last5=Matsuda |first5=Naoto |last6=Mishina |first6=Masayoshi |journal=Developmental Cell |volume=7 |pages=133–44 |pmid=15239961 |issue=1}}</ref>

====透明体色====
2008年，美國[[波士頓兒童醫院|波士頓兒童醫院]]的研究人员开发了一种新的斑马鱼品系Casper。这种品系的成鱼体色透明。<ref name=zviv/>这能够方便对细胞活动、循环系统[[遠端轉移|遠端轉移]]等现象的细致观察。由于人和斑马鱼有许多基因功能是相同的Casper品种被寄予加深人类对如白血病等癌症在内的人类疾病研究的厚望。<ref name=zviv/>在2013年1月，日本科学家转基因透明斑马鱼品系得到可以在高强度脑活动时放出可见发光的品系，使得斑马鱼对外界刺激的反应可以被记录精确到特定的大脑发光区域。<ref name=ithinkz>{{cite web|url=http://www.popsci.com/science/article/2013-01/watch-zebrafish-think-about-food|title=Researchers Capture A Zebrafish's Thought Process On Video|work=Popular Science|date=January 31, 2013|accessdate=February 4, 2013|archive-date=2016-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161003135509/http://www.popsci.com/science/article/2013-01/watch-zebrafish-think-about-food|dead-url=no}}</ref>

====环境监测====
2007年1月，[[复旦大学|复旦大学]]研究人员修改了斑马鱼的基因，使得其能够用于探测水体中的[[雌激素|雌激素]]污染，这一污染被认为与男性不育有关。研究人员克隆了对[[雌激素|雌激素]]敏感的基因，将之注入斑马鱼的受精卵中，得到的转基因鱼会在感知污染时变绿。<ref name=ChinaOest>[http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2007-01/12/content_5597696.htm "Fudan scientists turn fish into estrogen alerts"] {{Wayback|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2007-01/12/content_5597696.htm |date=20080225200714 }}. [[新华社|Xinhua]]. January 12, 2007. Retrieved November 15, 2012.</ref>

====RNA剪接====
2015年，美國[[布朗大学|布朗大学]]的研究人员发现，10%的斑马鱼基因并不依赖于{{link-en|U2AF2|U2AF2}}[[蛋白质|蛋白质]]来启动[[RNA剪接|RNA剪接]]。这些基因在每个[[内含子|内含子]]的尾端有着AC和TG碱基对的重复序列。在3'剪接位置(3' splicing site，简称3'ss)上，[[腺嘌呤|腺嘌呤]]（A）和[[胞嘧啶|胞嘧啶]]（C）交替重复 ；在5'剪接位置(5' splicing site，简称5'ss)上，互补的[[胸腺嘧啶|胸腺嘧啶]]（T）和[[鳥嘌呤|鳥嘌呤]]（G）同样交替重复。研究人员发现，斑马鱼对U2AF2蛋白的依赖比人类更小，而这一蛋白对RNA剪接的发生是必需的。这种在内含子周围重复碱基对以改变RNA{{link-en|二级结构|nucleic acid secondary structure}}的模式在[[真骨类|真骨类]]中曾发现过，但在[[四足類|四足類]]中未曾发现过。这表明[[四足類|四足類]]中的某一进化可能导致了人类与斑马鱼在对U2AF2依赖程度的差异。<ref name="BrownRNA">{{cite journal|last1=Lin|first1=Chien-Ling|last2=Taggart|first2=Allison J.|last3=Lim|first3=Kian Huat|last4=Cygan|first4=Kamil J.|last5=Ferraris|first5=Luciana|last6=Creton|first6=Robert|last7=Huang|first7=Yen-Tsung|last8=Fairbrother|first8=William G.|title=RNA structure replaces the need for U2AF2 in splicing|journal=Genome Research|date=13 November 2015|volume=26|issue=1|pages=12–23|pmid= 26566657|doi=10.1101/gr.181008.114|pmc=4691745}}</ref>

===近交衰退===
近亲交配后，幼鱼会显现近交衰退的不良后果。近交衰退主要由有害隐性基因的表达产生的。<ref name="pmid19834483">{{cite journal |vauthors=Charlesworth D, Willis JH |title=The genetics of inbreeding depression |journal=Nat. Rev. Genet. |volume=10 |issue=11 |pages=783–96 |year=2009 |pmid=19834483 |doi=10.1038/nrg2664 |url=}}</ref>对于斑马鱼而言，在较为紧张的环境（例如人为因素造成的紧张）中，近交衰退被认为会更加严重。由化学药剂克霉唑（一种咪唑类抗真菌类药物，用于农业、兽医、医疗）诱导的斑马鱼环境压力感受会加剧近亲繁殖在关键生育特性上的影响。<ref name="pmid23798977">{{cite journal |vauthors=Bickley LK, Brown AR, Hosken DJ, Hamilton PB, Le Page G, Paull GC, Owen SF, Tyler CR |title=Interactive effects of inbreeding and endocrine disruption on reproduction in a model laboratory fish |journal=Evol Appl |volume=6 |issue=2 |pages=279–89 |year=2013 |pmid=23798977 |pmc=3689353 |doi=10.1111/j.1752-4571.2012.00288.x |url=}}</ref>胚胎有效率在近亲杂交的鱼中大大减小，并且雄鱼产生后代有减少趋势。

==医学研究方向==
===癌症===
斑马鱼被用来生产包括[[黑色素瘤|黑色素瘤]]、[[白血病|白血病]]、[[胰腺癌|胰腺癌]]和[[肝細胞癌|肝細胞癌]]等癌症研究时使用的转基因模型。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Zebrafish models for cancer|work=Annu. Rev. Pathol.|year=2011|pmid=21261518|doi=10.1146/annurev-pathol-011110-130330|volume=6|pages=71–93|author1=Liu|first1=S|last2=Leach|first2=S. D.}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2011/03/110323141852.htm|title=Zebrafish model of human melanoma reveals new cancer gene|publisher=Science Daily|date=March 23, 2011|accessdate=April 28, 2014|archive-date=2019-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191210130405/https://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2011/03/110323141852.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>表达突变的BRAF或NRAS[[癌基因|癌基因]]的斑马鱼模型在置于缺乏[[p53|肿瘤抑制蛋白（p53）]]的背景下会得上[[黑色素瘤|黑色素瘤]]。在[[组织学|组织学]]上，这些肿瘤高度类似于人类疾病，是可移植入人体的，并且展现了大范围的基因组变化。BRAF基因[[黑色素瘤|黑色素瘤]]模型鱼被用来作两种筛选的平台，这一方法公布于2011年3月的《[[自然_(期刊)|自然]]》上。在另外一项研究中，这一模型被用来理解人类[[黑色素瘤|黑色素瘤]]中扩增和过表达的基因的功能作用。<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1038/nature09806 |title=The histone methyltransferase SETDB1 is recurrently amplified in melanoma and accelerates its onset |year=2011 |last1=Ceol |first1=Craig J. |last2=Houvras |first2=Yariv |last3=Jane-Valbuena |first3=Judit |last4=Bilodeau |first4=Steve |last5=Orlando |first5=David A. |last6=Battisti |first6=Valentine |last7=Fritsch |first7=Lauriane |last8=Lin |first8=William M. |last9=Hollmann |first9=Travis J. |last10=Ferré |first10=Fabrizio |last11=Bourque |first11=Caitlin |last12=Burke |first12=Christopher J. |last13=Turner |first13=Laura |last14=Uong |first14=Audrey |last15=Johnson |first15=Laura A. |last16=Beroukhim |first16=Rameen |last17=Mermel |first17=Craig H. |last18=Loda |first18=Massimo |last19=Ait-Si-Ali |first19=Slimane |last20=Garraway |first20=Levi A. |last21=Young |first21=Richard A. |last22=Zon |first22=Leonard I. |journal=Nature |volume=471 |issue=7339 |pages=513–7 |pmid=21430779 |pmc=3348545|display-authors=8 |bibcode=2011Natur.471..513C }}</ref>SETDB1基因能在斑马鱼体内显著地加速肿瘤生成，从而显示了其作为致癌基因的性质。这一点尤为重要，因为目前已知SETDB1参与了表观遗传调控，而表观遗传调控越发地被认为是肿瘤细胞生物学的核心。

在别的研究中，研究人员使用化学筛查，来针对起源[[神經脊|神經脊]]细胞中的遗传程序进行靶向治疗。<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1038/nature09882 |title=DHODH modulates transcriptional elongation in the neural crest and melanoma |year=2011 |last1=White |first1=Richard Mark |last2=Cech |first2=Jennifer |last3=Ratanasirintrawoot |first3=Sutheera |last4=Lin |first4=Charles Y. |last5=Rahl |first5=Peter B. |last6=Burke |first6=Christopher J. |last7=Langdon |first7=Erin |last8=Tomlinson |first8=Matthew L. |last9=Mosher |first9=Jack |last10=Kaufman |first10=Charles |last11=Chen |first11=Frank |last12=Long |first12=Hannah K. |last13=Kramer |first13=Martin |last14=Datta |first14=Sumon |last15=Neuberg |first15=Donna |last16=Granter |first16=Scott |last17=Young |first17=Richard A. |last18=Morrison |first18=Sean |last19=Wheeler |first19=Grant N. |last20=Zon |first20=Leonard I. |journal=Nature |volume=471 |issue=7339 |pages=518–22 |pmid=21430780|display-authors=8 |pmc=3759979 |bibcode=2011Natur.471..518W }}</ref>这项研究显示，一种叫做来氟米特（leflunomide）的的小分子抑制DHODH蛋白可以阻止[[神經脊|神經脊]]干细胞的发育，通过干涉{{link-en|转录延伸|Transcription_(biology)#Elongation}}能够避免这一发育最终所导致的[[黑色素瘤|黑色素瘤]]的发生。因为这一过程会针对性识别[[黑色素瘤|黑色素瘤]]而非其它单一的遗传变异，来氟米特可能在人类[[黑色素瘤|黑色素瘤]]治疗方面有所利用价值。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2011/03/110323141838.htm|title=Arthritis Drug Could Help Beat Melanoma Skin Cancer, Study Finds|publisher=Science Daily|date=March 24, 2011|accessdate=November 15, 2012|archive-date=2019-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191210130432/https://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2011/03/110323141838.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===心血管疾病===
在心血管研究领域，斑马鱼被用来模拟[[凝血|凝血]]、[[血管新生|血管新生]]、心脏衰竭和[[先天性心臟病|先天性心臟病]]。<ref>{{Cite journal|pmid=15647335|title=Kidney development and disease in the zebrafish|publisher=NCBI|year=2005|doi=10.1681/ASN.2004090754|volume=16|issue=2|journal=J. Am. Soc. Nephrol.|pages=299–304|author1=Drummond|first1=I. A.}}</ref>

===免疫系统===
研究急性[[炎症|炎症]]中，研究人员已经建立了炎症研究的斑马鱼模型以及相关处理机制，使得研究人员能对炎症的遗传控制机制进行细化研究，并且有可能以此识别有潜力的新药物。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fishforscience.com/disease/inflammatory-disease|title=Investigating inflammatory disease using zebrafish|publisher=Fish For Science|accessdate=November 15, 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130109005739/http://www.fishforscience.com/disease/inflammatory-disease|archivedate=2013年1月9日|df=}}</ref>

斑马鱼在研究脊椎动物的固有免疫方面是广泛使用的[[模式生物|模式生物]]（固有免疫能够在受精后28～30小时内进行吞噬作用，[[吞噬作用|吞噬作用]]是免疫反应的重要一环）。<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Guyader|first=Dorothée Le|last2=Redd|first2=Michael J.|last3=Colucci-Guyon|first3=Emma|last4=Murayama|first4=Emi|last5=Kissa|first5=Karima|last6=Briolat|first6=Valérie|last7=Mordelet|first7=Elodie|last8=Zapata|first8=Agustin|last9=Shinomiya|first9=Hiroto|date=2008-01-01|title=Origins and unconventional behavior of neutrophils in developing zebrafish|url=http://www.bloodjournal.org/content/111/1/132|journal=Blood|language=en|volume=111|issue=1|pages=132–141|doi=10.1182/blood-2007-06-095398|issn=0006-4971|pmid=17875807|access-date=2018-02-13|archive-date=2019-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190911142654/http://www.bloodjournal.org/content/111/1/132|dead-url=no}}</ref>与之对比，[[适应性免疫|适应性免疫]]（也称特异性免疫、获得性免疫、后天性免疫）在受精后至少四周才能在功能上达到成熟状态。<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-1-4614-0106-3_15|title=Current Topics in Innate Immunity II|last=Novoa|first=Beatriz|last2=Figueras|first2=Antonio|date=2012-01-01|publisher=Springer New York|isbn=9781461401056|editor-last=Lambris|editor-first=John D.|series=Advances in Experimental Medicine and Biology|pages=253–275|language=en|doi=10.1007/978-1-4614-0106-3_15|editor-last2=Hajishengallis|editor-first2=George|access-date=2018-02-13|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809190729/https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-1-4614-0106-3_15|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===传染病===
由于人类和斑马鱼的免疫系统保守性较强、相对一致性高，许多人类传染病可以在斑马鱼上模拟。<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Meeker | first1 = Nathan D. | last2 = Trede Nikolaus | first2 = S. | year = 2008 | title = Immunology and zebrafish: spawning new models of human disease | url = | journal = Dev Comp Immunol | volume = 32 | issue = 7| pages = 745–757 | doi = 10.1016/j.dci.2007.11.011 | pmid = 18222541 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Renshaw | first1 = S.A. | last2 = Trede | first2 = N.S. | year = 2012 | title = A model 450 million years in the making: zebrafish and vertebrate immunity | url = | journal = Dis Model Mech | volume = 5 | issue = 1| pages = 38–47 | doi = 10.1242/dmm.007138 | pmid = 22228790 | pmc = 3255542 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Meijer | first1 = A.H. | last2 = Spaink | first2 = H.P. | year = 2011 | title = Host–pathogen interactions made transparent with the zebrafish model | url = | journal = Curr Drug Targets | volume = 12 | issue = 7| pages = 1000–1017 | doi = 10.2174/138945011795677809 | pmid = 21366518 | pmc = 3319919 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Van der Vaart | first1 = M | last2 = Spaink | first2 = HP | last3 = Meijer | first3 = AH | year = 2012 | title = Pathogen recognition and activation of the innate immune response in zebra fish | url = | journal = Adv Hematol | volume = 2012 | issue = | page = 159807 | doi = 10.1155/2012/159807 | pmid = 22811714 | pmc = 3395205 }}</ref>斑马鱼透明的早期胚胎被用于深入研究活体成像和分析宿主和病原体之间的互动。<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Benard | first1 = EL | last2 = Van Der Sar | first2 = AM | last3 = Ellett | first3 = F | last4 = Lieschke | first4 = GJ | last5 = Spaink | first5 = HP | last6 = Meijer | first6 = AH | year = 2012 | title = Infection of zebrafish embryos with intracellular bacterial pathogens | url = | journal = J Vis Exp. | volume = | issue = 61| pages = | doi = 10.3791/3781 | pmid = 22453760 | pmc = 3415172 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Meijer | first1 = AH | last2 = van der Vaart | first2 = M | last3 = Spaink | first3 = HP | year = 2013 | title = Real-time imaging and genetic dissection of host-microbe interactions in zebrafish | url = | journal = Cell Microbiol | volume = 16| issue = 1| pages = 39–49| doi = 10.1111/cmi.12236 | pmid = 24188444 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Torraca | first1 = V | last2 = Masud | first2 = S | last3 = Spaink | first3 = HP | last4 = Meijer | first4 = AH | date = Jul 2014 | title = Macrophage-pathogen interactions in infectious diseases: new therapeutic insights from the zebrafish host model | url = | journal = Dis Model Mech. | volume = 7 | issue = 7| pages = 785–97 | doi = 10.1242/dmm.015594 | pmid = 24973749 | pmc=4073269}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Levraud | first1 = JP | last2 = Palha | first2 = N | last3 = Langevin | first3 = C | last4 = Boudinot | first4 = P | date = Sep 2014 | title = Through the looking glass: witnessing host-virus interplay in zebrafish | url = | journal = Trends Microbiol | volume = 22 | issue = 9| pages = 490–7 | doi = 10.1016/j.tim.2014.04.014 | pmid = 24865811 }}</ref>科学家已经建立了用于模拟一大批细菌、病毒、寄生虫类病原体的斑马鱼模型，例如用于结核病研究的斑马鱼模型已经为分支杆菌的致病机制研究提供了深入研究的平台。<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Ramakrishnan | first1 = L | year = 2013 | title = Looking within the zebrafish to understand the tuberculous granuloma | url = | journal = Adv Exp Med Biol. | volume = 783 | issue = | pages = 251–66 | doi = 10.1007/978-1-4614-6111-1_13 | pmid = 23468113 | series = Advances in Experimental Medicine and Biology | isbn = 978-1-4614-6110-4 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Ramakrishnan | first1 = L | year = 2013 | title = The zebrafish guide to tuberculosis immunity and treatment | url = | journal = Cold Spring Harb Symp Quant Biol. | volume = 78 | issue = | pages = 179–92 | doi = 10.1101/sqb.2013.78.023283 | pmid = 24643219 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Cronan | first1 = MR | last2 = Tobin | first2 = DM | date = Jul 2014 | title = Fit for consumption: zebrafish as a model for tuberculosis | url = | journal = Dis Model Mech. | volume = 7 | issue = 7| pages = 777–84 | doi = 10.1242/dmm.016089 | pmid = 24973748 | pmc=4073268}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Meijer | first1 = AH | year = 2015 | title = Protection and pathology in TB: learning from the zebrafish model | url = | journal = Semin Immunopathol | volume = 38| issue = 2| pages = 261–73 | page = | doi = 10.1007/s00281-015-0522-4 | pmid = 26324465 | pmc = 4779130 }}</ref>此外，也已经发展出使用斑马鱼感染模型进行高通量微抗生素药物筛查的自动化技术。<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Spaink | first1 = HP | last2 = Cui | first2 = C | last3 = Wiweger | first3 = MI | last4 = Jansen | first4 = HJ | last5 = Veneman | first5 = WJ | last6 = Marín-Juez | first6 = R | last7 = de Sonneville | first7 = J | last8 = Ordas | first8 = A | last9 = Torraca | first9 = V | last10 = van der Ent | first10 = W | last11 = Leenders | first11 = WP | last12 = Meijer | first12 = AH | last13 = Snaar-Jagalska | first13 = BE | last14 = Dirks | first14 = RP | date = Aug 2013 | title = Robotic injection of zebrafish embryos for high-throughput screening in disease models | url = | journal = Methods | volume = 62 | issue = 3| pages = 246–54 | doi = 10.1016/j.ymeth.2013.06.002 | pmid = 23769806 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Veneman | first1 = WJ | last2 = Marín-Juez | first2 = R | last3 = de Sonneville | first3 = J | last4 = Ordas | first4 = A | last5 = Jong-Raadsen | first5 = S | last6 = Meijer | first6 = AH | last7 = Spaink | first7 = HP | date = Jun 2014 | title = Establishment and optimization of a high throughput setup to study Staphylococcus epidermidis and Mycobacterium marinum infection as a model for drug discovery | url = | journal = J Vis Exp. | volume = 88 | issue = 88| page = e51649 | doi = 10.3791/51649 | pmid = 24998295 | pmc=4206090}}</ref>

===修复视网膜损伤===
[[File:Development_of_the_retina.tif|thumb]]
斑马鱼的另一显著特征在于其拥有四种[[视锥细胞|视锥细胞]]，除人体内拥有的红色、绿色、蓝色敏感视锥细胞外，拥有[[紫外线|紫外线]]敏感细胞。斑马鱼因此可以看见非常广的色谱。故斑马鱼也被用于研究视网膜的发育，尤其是视锥细胞如何在视网膜中形成镶嵌方面。斑马鱼和一些[[真骨类|真骨类]]鱼类以其视网膜上高度精密的视锥细胞镶嵌排列备受科学家关注。<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1002/cne.22447 |title=Ontogeny of cone photoreceptor mosaics in zebrafish |year=2010 |last1=Allison |first1=W. Ted |last2=Barthel |first2=Linda K. |last3=Skebo |first3=Kristina M. |last4=Takechi |first4=Masaki |last5=Kawamura |first5=Shoji |last6=Raymond |first6=Pamela A. |journal=The Journal of Comparative Neurology |volume=518 |issue=20 |pages=4182–95 |pmid=20878782 |pmc=3376642}}</ref>

这一对斑马鱼视网膜特性的研究也已经延展至人类的视网膜医学研究。2007年，[[伦敦大学学院|伦敦大学学院]]的研究人员培养出一种成年斑马鱼[[幹細胞|幹細胞]]，这些干细胞在斑马鱼和哺乳动物的眼睛中被发现，且最终会发育成视网膜[[神經元|神经]]。这些细胞可以注射进入眼部，用于治疗损坏视网膜神经的疾病，此类疾病涵盖大部分眼疾，包括[[黃斑部退化|黃斑部退化]]、[[青光眼|青光眼]]、[[糖尿病|糖尿病]]相关失明等。研究人员研究了人眼中的Müller[[神經膠質細胞|细胞]]，其研究对象年龄从18个月大到91岁。研究中，科研人员能够将这些细胞培养为所有种类的视网膜神经细胞。研究团队在实验室可以轻松地培育这些细胞，并且还将培育出的干细胞移植进入大鼠视网膜中对周围的神经进行观察，研究人员称这些干细胞试图以与在人体内相同的方式发育。<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1634/stemcells.2006-0724 |laysource=[[英文中國郵報|The China Post]] |laydate=August 3, 2007 |laysummary=http://www.chinapost.com.tw/health/eye%20health/2007/08/03/116860/Zebra-fish.htm |title=MIO-M1 Cells and Similar Müller Glial Cell Lines Derived from Adult Human Retina Exhibit Neural Stem Cell Characteristics |year=2007 |last1=Lawrence |first1=Jean M. |last2=Singhal |first2=Shweta |last3=Bhatia |first3=Bhairavi |last4=Keegan |first4=David J. |last5=Reh |first5=Thomas A. |last6=Luthert |first6=Philip J. |last7=Khaw |first7=Peng T. |last8=Limb |first8=Gloria Astrid |journal=Stem Cells |volume=25 |issue=8 |pages=2033–43 |pmid=17525239}}</ref>

===药物研发===
如同在许多进行中的研究项目所演示的那样，斑马鱼模型使得研究者不仅能够识别除引发人类疾病的基因，也可以用来在药物开发项目中开发新的治疗药剂。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.fishforscience.com/ |title=Fish for Science |publisher=University of Sheffield |year=2011 |accessdate=March 19, 2011 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112013436/https://fishforscience.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>斑马鱼胚胎是一种快速、性价比高且可靠的[[畸形学|致畸]]检验模型。<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1002/bdrb.20223 |title=Development of a zebrafish embryo teratogenicity assay and quantitative prediction model |year=2010 |last1=Brannen |first1=Kimberly C. |last2=Panzica-Kelly |first2=Julieta M. |last3=Danberry |first3=Tracy L. |last4=Augustine-Rauch |first4=Karen A. |journal=Birth Defects Research Part B: Developmental and Reproductive Toxicology |volume=89 |pmid=20166227 |pages=66–77 |issue=1}}</ref>使用斑马鱼进行药物筛查可以识别具有生物学疗效的新的化合物种类，或者发现已知药物的新用途。例如一种常用的抑制剂（[[瑞舒伐他汀|瑞舒伐他汀]]）通过斑马鱼试验发现可以抑制[[前列腺癌|前列腺癌]]的生长。<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Rennekamp|first=Andrew J|last2=Peterson|first2=Randall T|date=2015-02-01|title=15 years of zebrafish chemical screening|url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1367593114001653|journal=Current Opinion in Chemical Biology|series=Omics|volume=24|pages=58–70|doi=10.1016/j.cbpa.2014.10.025|pmc=4339096|pmid=25461724}}</ref>迄今为止，已经进行过65项小分子筛查，其中至少一项已经进行临床试验。<ref name=":0">{{Cite journal|last=MacRae|first=Calum A.|last2=Peterson|first2=Randall T.|title=Zebrafish as tools for drug discovery|url=http://www.nature.com/doifinder/10.1038/nrd4627|journal=Nature Reviews Drug Discovery|volume=14|issue=10|pages=721–731|doi=10.1038/nrd4627|year=2015}}</ref>在这些筛查中，许多技术难度仍待解决，例如：药物吸收率在不同组织或者器官是不同的，这一不同导致药物的实际有效浓度（即其对特定部位的暴露量）无法从其水溶液浓度推算；个体动物之间的天然差异等。<ref name=":0" />但对于理解药效而言，药物的暴露产生了药效，因此了解药物在体内的暴露量是至关重要的。同时，将斑马鱼身上的实验结果解读为对人类等高等脊椎动物有效的结果需要在知悉药物浓度和药效之间的关系基础上，这一基础可由[[药物代谢动力学|药物代谢动力学]]和[[药物效应动力学|药物效应动力学]]方面分析产生。迄今，只有对于[[对乙酰氨基酚|对乙酰氨基酚]]的斑马鱼幼体模型已经建立了上述所言的人体和药物相互作用的模型。<ref>{{Cite journal
|last=Kantae|first=Vasudev|last2=Krekels|first2=Elke HJ|last3=Ordas|first3=Anita|last4=González|first4=Oskar|last5=Van Wijk|first5=Rob C|last6=Harms|first6=Amy C|last7=Racz|first7=Peter I|last8=Van der Graaf|first8=Piet H|last9=Spaink|first9=Herman P|last10=Hankemeier|first10=Thomas|title=Pharmacokinetic Modeling of Paracetamol Uptake and Clearance in Zebrafish Larvae: Expanding the Allometric Scale in Vertebrates with Five Orders of Magnitude|url=http://online.liebertpub.com/doi/10.1089/zeb.2016.1313|journal=Zebrafish|volume=13|issue=6|pages=504–510|doi=10.1089/zeb.2016.1313|pmid=27632065|year=2016|pmc=5124745}}</ref>但在斑马鱼身上进行药理学分析前景仍是广阔的。<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Van Wijk|first=Rob C|last2=Krekels|first2=Elke HJ|last3=Hankemeier|first3=Thomas|last4=Spaink|first4=Herman P|last5=Van der Graaf|first5=Piet H|title=Systems pharmacology of hepatic metabolism in zebrafish larvae|url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1740675717300191|journal=Drug Discovery Today Disease Models|doi=10.1016/j.ddmod.2017.04.003|year=2017|volume=22|pages=27–34|access-date=2018-02-13|archive-date=2021-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210715052044/https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1740675717300191|dead-url=no}}</ref>

